{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-base-page-js","path":"/ia/descartes/best-practice/03-rules/","result":{"data":{"pageContent":{"html":"<h1 id=\"best-practice-for-rules\">Best practice for rules</h1>\n<p>Rules should be used as a library of business filters for ledger data.<br>\nWhen adding filters to a view, prefer to use a rule instead:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Better performance (saved rule results);</li>\n<li>Reusesability (same rule used in different views);</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"definition\">Definition</h2>\n<p>Use the project/facet identifier as a prefix in the rule identifier and name.<br>\nUse the same <strong>naming rules</strong> for attributes as for views.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>See <code class=\"language-text\">Concept Prefixes</code> in <a href=\"./03-rules\">Views best practice</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Example rule:<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 798px; z-index: -1\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 66.54545454545455%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Sample rule\"\n        title=\"Sample rule\"\n        src=\"/static/790fd18ac3c095e99c476c2214597813/50208/guideline_sample_rule.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/790fd18ac3c095e99c476c2214597813/88b8e/guideline_sample_rule.png 275w,\n/static/790fd18ac3c095e99c476c2214597813/8c3ad/guideline_sample_rule.png 550w,\n/static/790fd18ac3c095e99c476c2214597813/50208/guideline_sample_rule.png 798w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 798px) 100vw, 798px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"saved-rules\">Saved rules</h2>\n<p>When reusing rules in views, it's better to use the saved rule result links in views, as it's faster.<br>\nFor instance:<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 522px; z-index: -1\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.45454545454546%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"View saved rules\"\n        title=\"View saved rules\"\n        src=\"/static/5d358dcf3ca4fc6b876dc5bd83ca575b/d15a3/guideline_view_saved_rule.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5d358dcf3ca4fc6b876dc5bd83ca575b/88b8e/guideline_view_saved_rule.png 275w,\n/static/5d358dcf3ca4fc6b876dc5bd83ca575b/d15a3/guideline_view_saved_rule.png 522w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 522px) 100vw, 522px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>You have to ensure that the rule is included in the execution plan:<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 462px; z-index: -1\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.636363636363633%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Rule execution plan\"\n        title=\"Rule execution plan\"\n        src=\"/static/fd5832e6d6a1f27ec8ddcc9880c72d22/a9e02/guideline_rule_execplan.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fd5832e6d6a1f27ec8ddcc9880c72d22/88b8e/guideline_rule_execplan.png 275w,\n/static/fd5832e6d6a1f27ec8ddcc9880c72d22/a9e02/guideline_rule_execplan.png 462w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 462px) 100vw, 462px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Note that this only applies to rules <strong>without parameters</strong>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"warnings\">Warnings</h3>\n<p>There is no dependency check between rules.<br>\nIf you want a main rule to use saved rule results from detail rules, the main rule cannot be saved in the execution plan!<br>\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 830px; z-index: -1\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.81818181818183%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Rule dependencies\"\n        title=\"Rule dependencies\"\n        src=\"/static/08e00c68b9efd098131d2d4d33211c49/026af/guideline_rule_saved_subrule.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/08e00c68b9efd098131d2d4d33211c49/88b8e/guideline_rule_saved_subrule.png 275w,\n/static/08e00c68b9efd098131d2d4d33211c49/8c3ad/guideline_rule_saved_subrule.png 550w,\n/static/08e00c68b9efd098131d2d4d33211c49/026af/guideline_rule_saved_subrule.png 830w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 830px) 100vw, 830px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h1","properties":{"id":"best-practice-for-rules"},"children":[{